    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with normal driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor aging on the control buttons. Mechanically, the car runs well and handles predictably, with all major systems functioning as intended. It represents a solid, dependable choice for someone looking for a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
