    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride. It's been super reliable and is still in really solid shape. It looks great and drives even better\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the new-car price tag. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
