    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six heritage. The powerplant features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip variable M differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
